<div class='container'>
<div class='m1 module'>
<nav class='breadcrumb m4 show-lg'>Watch&nbsp;&nbsp;&rsaquo;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a class="breadcrumb__link" href="/watch/topics" rel=" up">Topics</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&rsaquo;&nbsp;&nbsp;</nav>

<h1 class='h1 h1--alt m2'>
Cities
</h1>

</div>

<div class='row'>
<div class='col col-lg-sidebarred'>
<!-- PB:B: copy --><div class='p2'>
<p>More than half the world's population lives in cities. In these TED Talks, explore the crowded favelas, greened-up blocks and futuristic districts that will shape the future of cities -- and the future of humanity.</p>

</div>



<!-- PB:B: dynamic -->
<div class='section section--minor'>
<!--[if lte IE 8]>
<style>
@import url("https://tedcdnpa-a.akamaihd.net/stylesheets/pages/dynamic/topics-ie.css?1449612282");
</style>
<![endif]-->
<!--[if gt IE 8]><!-->
<style scoped>
