</style>
<!--<![endif]-->
<h3 class="h4 m3">Video playlists about Cities</h3>
<div class='row row-skinny row-sm-2up'>
<div class='col'>
<div class='m2'>
<h4 class='h7 m3'>Our future in cities</h4>
<div class='row row-skinny row-oh-2up'>
<div class='col'>
<a href='/playlists/29/our_future_in_cities'>
<span class="thumb thumb--square"><span class="thumb__sizer"><span class="thumb__tugger"><img alt="" class=" thumb__image" play="false" src="https://tedcdnpi-a.akamaihd.net/r/tedcdnpf-a.akamaihd.net/images/playlists/our_future_in_cities.jpg?quality=89&amp;w=256" /><span class="thumb__aligner"></span></span></span></span>
</a>
</div>
<div class='col'>
<div class='meta m4'>
15 talks
&bull;
<span class='meta__val'>3h 44m</span>
</div>
<div class='p4'>Humanity's future is the future of cities. Explore the crowded favelas, greened-up blocks and futuristic districts that could shape the future of cities -- and take a profane, hilarious side trip to the suburbs.</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class='col'>
<div class='m2'>
<h4 class='h7 m3'>Architectural inspiration</h4>
<div class='row row-skinny row-oh-2up'>
<div class='col'>
<a href='/playlists/25/architectural_inspiration'>
<span class="thumb thumb--square"><span class="thumb__sizer"><span class="thumb__tugger"><img alt="" class=" thumb__image" play="false" src="https://tedcdnpi-a.akamaihd.net/r/tedcdnpf-a.akamaihd.net/images/playlists/architectural_inspirations.jpg?quality=89&amp;w=256" /><span class="thumb__aligner"></span></span></span></span>
</a>
</div>
<div class='col'>
<div class='meta m4'>
9 talks
&bull;
<span class='meta__val'>2h 45m</span>
</div>
<div class='p4'>Master architects share their vision for buildings that inflate, float, twist and glitter, while artfully addressing the challenges faced by their residents, their cities and the planet.</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class='col'>
<div class='m2'>
<h4 class='h7 m3'>The big picture</h4>
<div class='row row-skinny row-oh-2up'>
<div class='col'>
<a href='/playlists/126/the_big_picture'>
<span class="thumb thumb--square"><span class="thumb__sizer"><span class="thumb__tugger"><img alt="" class=" thumb__image" play="false" src="https://tedcdnpi-a.akamaihd.net/r/tedcdnpf-a.akamaihd.net/images/playlists/the_big_picture.jpg?quality=89&amp;w=256" /><span class="thumb__aligner"></span></span></span></span>
</a>
</div>
<div class='col'>
<div class='meta m4'>
15 talks
&bull;
<span class='meta__val'>4h 18m</span>
</div>
<div class='p4'>Must-listen talks about the future of the environment, crime, technology, government and the human race.</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class='col'>
<div class='m2'>
<h4 class='h7 m3'>Talks to give you wanderlust</h4>
<div class='row row-skinny row-oh-2up'>
<div class='col'>
<a href='/playlists/172/talks_to_give_you_wanderlust'>
<span class="thumb thumb--square"><span class="thumb__sizer"><span class="thumb__tugger"><img alt="" class=" thumb__image" play="false" src="https://tedcdnpi-a.akamaihd.net/r/tedcdnpf-a.akamaihd.net/images/playlists/talks_to_give_you_wanderlust.jpg?quality=89&amp;w=256" /><span class="thumb__aligner"></span></span></span></span>
</a>
</div>
<div class='col'>
<div class='meta m4'>
9 talks
&bull;
<span class='meta__val'>1h 59m</span>
</div>
<div class='p4'>Prepare to be swept away with longing for distant places. Hit play on these talks while you pack your bags for an epic journey.</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
